Summary Information

Repository
Detroit Public Library
Title
Civic Searchlight records
ID
03435
Date
1913-1995
Extent
109.0 linear ft.
General Physical Description note
(216 boxes, 1 volume)
Language
English
Abstract
Profiles of candidates from Wayne, Oakland and Macomb Counties. Also includes papers for affiliate organizations of Civic, Inc., Oakland Citizens league and Macomb County Division.

Administrative Information

Publication Information

Detroit Public Library Feb. 17, 2010

Conditions Governing Access note

This collection is open for research use.
